text:
GET parameters are missing in access log. ie, the log has entries like this:

82.213.136.185 - - [24/Jul/2001:12:03:27 00] "GET /foo/bar/baz HTTP/1.1" 200 
30995

instead of:

82.213.136.185 - - [24/Jul/2001:12:03:27 00] "GET /foo/bar/baz?id=16&page=2 
HTTP/1.1" 200 30995
creator: colin@london.virgin.net
